  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/18",
  "title": "IE >= 8 Support",
  "body": "> Since Babel assumes that your code will be ran in an ES5 environment it uses ES5 functions. So if you're using an environment that has limited or no support for ES5 such as lower versions of IE then using the es5-shim along with the Babel polyfill will add support for these methods.\n\nhttps://babeljs.io/docs/advanced/caveats/\n",
